            {src: "assets/shops/toy-shop.png", name: "Toy Shop", desc: "Enter a realm of enchantment at our Toy Shop, where imagination knows no bounds and every shelf holds the promise of endless play. Step into a world of whimsy and wonder as you discover a curated collection of toys that inspire creativity, ignite laughter, and bring joy to hearts both young and young at heart."}, 
            {src: "assets/shops/gift-shop.png", name: "Gift Shop", desc: "Embark on a journey of discovery as you step into our Gift Shop, where every shelf is a treasure trove of delights waiting to be unwrapped. Immerse yourself in a world of charming trinkets, unique souvenirs, and carefully curated gifts that capture the spirit of your theme park adventure."}].forEach(function(elem){ %>
